| Origin                  = [[Victor von Doom (Earth-616)|Doctor Doom]] designed these robots as a patrol for [[Doomstadt]], a means to protect [[Latveria]] from foreign invasions and a law enforcement. They are good at controlling the population and finding and defeating intruders. <br>
